---
title: Roasted Sweet Potatoes with Crispy Spiced Chickpeas
description: Humble chickpeas are upgraded to a whole new level with a quick roast in the oven. Creamy, lemony hummus and roasted sweet potatoes provide the ideal vehicle for these crispy gems. They might be your new go-to snack.
